# GRAPHICS::SET_PARTICLE_FX_SLIPSTREAM_LODRANGE_SCALE

## Summary
Sets the range/lod scale used for the slipstream effects (set to 1.0 for authored range/lods)

## Parameters
* **FLOAT** scale
